OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778000754
OL,3,CPalestine Action activists found
OL,4,Cguilty of criminal damage over factory
OL,5,Craid
OL,7,FFour Palestine Action activists have
OL,8,Fbeen found guilty of criminal damage
OL,9,Fafter raiding an Israel-based defence
OL,10,Ffirm's UK site and destroying
OL,11,Fequipment with sledgehammers and
OL,12,Fcrowbars in a bid to shut the factory
OL,13,Fdown.
OL,15,FOne of the group was also found guilty
OL,16,Fof assault causing grievous bodily
OL,17,Fharm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
