PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778000754
OL,3,CPalestine Action activists found
OL,4,Cguilty of criminal damage over factory
OL,5,Craid
OL,7,FCharlotte Head, Samuel Corner, Leona
OL,8,FKamio and Fatema Rajwani were in a
OL,9,Fprison van which crashed into shutters
OL,10,Fat the Elbit Systems factory in
OL,11,FBristol in the early hours of August 6
OL,12,F2024, Woolwich Crown Court was told.
OL,14,FThe activists, all wearing red
OL,15,Fboilersuits, then set about destroying
OL,16,Fproperty inside the factory, before
OL,17,Fclashing with security guards and
OL,18,Fpolice who tried to stop the raid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778000754
OL,3,CPalestine Action activists found
OL,4,Cguilty of criminal damage over factory
OL,5,Craid
OL,7,FHead, 30, was driving the prison van
OL,8,Fwhich was used as a "battering ram" to
OL,9,Fbreak into the facility, the court
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FThe raid had been "meticulously
OL,13,Forganised" and was aimed at "causing
OL,14,Fas much damage as possible and obtain
OL,15,Finformation about the company", said
OL,16,Fprosecutor Deanna Heer KC.
OL,26,@pD@UOUpD@cO]tD@SOUuD@JO]uD@]OUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
