CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778000754
OL,3,CPalestine Action activists found
OL,4,Cguilty of criminal damage over factory
OL,5,Craid
OL,7,FThe activists used sledgehammers and
OL,8,Fcrowbars they had brought with them to
OL,9,Fdestroy computers, drones, and other
OL,10,Fequipment, and used fire extinguishers
OL,11,Fto spray red paint across the walls
OL,12,Fand floor.
OL,14,FThe group caused an estimated #1
OL,15,Fmillion of damage during the raid, a
OL,16,Fcourt was told.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
