FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778000754
OL,3,CPalestine Action activists found
OL,4,Cguilty of criminal damage over factory
OL,5,Craid
OL,7,FHead, Corner, Kamio and Rajwani were
OL,8,Feach found guilty of criminal damage
OL,9,Fafter a jury deliberated for more than
OL,10,F14 hours.
OL,12,FTwo other activists, Zoe Rogers and
OL,13,FJordan Devlin, who had been charged
OL,14,Fwith criminal damage, were found not
OL,15,Fguilty.
OL,17,FCorner was also found guilty of
OL,18,Finflicting grievous bodily harm by a
OL,19,Fmajority of 11 to one. He was cleared
OL,20,Fof grievous bodily harm with intent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
