PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778000754
OL,3,CPalestine Action activists found
OL,4,Cguilty of criminal damage over factory
OL,5,Craid
OL,7,FThe government had previously lost a
OL,8,Fcourt case against their decision to
OL,9,Fproscribe Palestine Action as a
OL,10,Fterrorist group.
OL,12,FA decision from the Court of Appeal
OL,13,Fover whether this previous ruling
OL,14,Fagainst the government can stand is
OL,15,Fexpected at a later date after
OL,16,Farguments concluded last week.
OL,18,FPalestine Action will remain a
OL,19,Fproscribed group until the appeal
OL,20,Fdecision is heard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
